pact of environmental factors. <a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/14972079?ordinalpos=1&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_DefaultReportPanel.Pubmed_RVDocSum\" target=\"_blank\"></a>Int J Neuro psychopharmacol. 2004;7(Suppl 1):S7&ndash;S13.</li>\n<li id=\"reference_8\">Kelly BD, Feeney L, O\\qCallaghan E, Browne R, <br> Byrne M, Mulryan N, et al. Obstetric adversity and age at first presentation with schizophrenia: Evidence of a dose-response relationship.<br><a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15121662?ordinalpos=1&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_DefaultReportPanel.Pubmed_RVDocSum\" target=\"_blank\">Am J Psychiatry. 2004;161:920&ndash;2.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_9\">Tsapakisa, AM, Guillinb O, Murray RM. Does <a href=\"/atclist/C01CA04\" data-atcid=\"C01CA04\" data-atctitles=\"Hj&#xE4;rta_och_kretslopp--Medel_vid_hj&#xE4;rtsjukdomar--Hj&#xE4;rtstimulerande_medel_exkl._hj&#xE4;rtglykosider--Adrenerga_och_dopaminerga_medel--Dopamin\" class=\"inlineGenerica text\">dopamin</a>e sensitization underlie the association between schizophrenia and drug abuse? <a href=\"http://www.psycnet.org/index.cfm?fa=search.displayRecord&amp;uid=2003-06655-010\" target=\"_blank\">Current </a> Opinion in Psychiatry. 2003;16 (Suppl 2): S45&ndash;S52</li>\n<li id=\"reference_10\">Zammit S, Allebeck P, Andreasson S, Lundberg I, Lewis G. Self reported cannabis use as a risk factor for schizophrenia in Swedish conscripts of 1969: historical cohort study. <br><a href=\"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/12446534?ordinalpos=11&amp;itool=EntrezSystem2.PEntrez.Pubmed.Pubmed_ResultsPanel.Pubmed_DefaultReportPanel.Pubmed_RVDocSum\" target=\"_blank\">BMJ. 2002;325:1199&ndash;1201.</a></li>\n<li id=\"reference_11\">Caspi A, Moffitt TE, Cannon M, McClay J, Murray R, Harrington H, et al. Moderation of the effect of adolescent-onset cannabis use on adult psychosis by a functional polymorphism in the catechol-O-methylt